### 2.2. WebSocket Server — Docker Container (Port 3001)

> Container: `kirimart-ws` | Image: `kirimart-ws-server` (Node.js 22 Alpine, ~60MB)

**Entry point:** [ws-server/src/index.js](file:///c:/Putra/Ngoding%20AntiGravity/set-ecomerce/kirimart/ws-server/src/index.js)

**Fungsi utama:**

1. **Socket.IO WebSocket Server** — koneksi real-time dari browser
2. **Express REST API** — endpoint `/emit` dan `/jobs/schedule` untuk Next.js
3. **Redis Adapter** — scaling multi-instance 
4. **BullMQ Workers** — background job processor

**Namespace WebSocket:**

| Namespace | File | Fungsi |
|-----------|------|--------|
| `/chat` | [chat.js](file:///c:/Putra/Ngoding%20AntiGravity/set-ecomerce/kirimart/ws-server/src/namespaces/chat.js) | Real-time chat (join room, send message, typing indicator) |
| `/notifications` | [notifications.js](file:///c:/Putra/Ngoding%20AntiGravity/set-ecomerce/kirimart/ws-server/src/namespaces/notifications.js) | Push notifications (new-order, order-status, dll) |

**REST Endpoints:**

| Endpoint | File | Fungsi |
|----------|------|--------|
| `POST /emit` | [emit.js](file:///c:/Putra/Ngoding%20AntiGravity/set-ecomerce/kirimart/ws-server/src/api/emit.js) | Next.js → WS broadcast ke browser |
| `POST /jobs/schedule` | [jobs.js](file:///c:/Putra/Ngoding%20AntiGravity/set-ecomerce/kirimart/ws-server/src/api/jobs.js) | Jadwalkan background job (BullMQ) |
| `GET /jobs/stats` | [jobs.js](file:///c:/Putra/Ngoding%20AntiGravity/set-ecomerce/kirimart/ws-server/src/api/jobs.js) | Status antrian jobs |
| `GET /health` | [index.js](file:///c:/Putra/Ngoding%20AntiGravity/set-ecomerce/kirimart/ws-server/src/index.js) | Docker healthcheck |

**Autentikasi WS:**
- Setiap koneksi WebSocket harus mengirim `sessionToken` via `socket.handshake.auth`
- WS Server memverifikasi token dengan query langsung ke tabel `session` di PostgreSQL
- Koneksi ditolak jika token tidak valid atau expired
- Menggunakan `host.docker.internal` untuk akses PostgreSQL di Windows host dari dalam container

**BullMQ Workers** ([worker.js](file:///c:/Putra/Ngoding%20AntiGravity/set-ecomerce/kirimart/ws-server/src/jobs/worker.js)):

| Queue | Job | Delay | Fungsi |
|-------|-----|-------|--------|
| `kawanbelanja-orders` | `auto-complete` | 7 hari | Auto-complete order + tambah saldo seller |
| `kawanbelanja-payments` | `expire-payment` | 24 jam | Cancel order & restore stok jika belum bayar |
| `kawanbelanja-scoring` | `recalculate-scores` | Cron setiap 6 jam | Hitung ulang visibility score (Fair Rank) |

