> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Perbedaan penting koneksi di dalam Docker vs Host:**
> - **WS Server (di Docker)** mengakses PostgreSQL via `host.docker.internal:5432`
> - **WS Server (di Docker)** mengakses Redis via `redis:6379` (Docker service name)
> - **Next.js (di Host)** mengakses semua via `localhost` (6379, 3001, 5432)

**Startup order:**
1. `redis` start dulu → healthcheck `redis-cli ping`
2. `ws-server` start **setelah** Redis healthy (depends_on + condition)
3. Next.js di-start **manual** dari host (`bun dev`)

**Dockerfile WS Server** ([Dockerfile](file:///c:/Putra/Ngoding%20AntiGravity/set-ecomerce/kirimart/ws-server/Dockerfile)):
- Multi-stage build (deps → runner)
- Production-only dependencies (`npm install --omit=dev`)
- Image final ~60MB
- Healthcheck: `wget http://localhost:3001/health` setiap 30 detik

