## 4. Alur Data End-to-End

### 4.1. Alur Pembayaran (Midtrans)

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant B as Browser
    participant N as Next.js
    participant M as Midtrans
    participant WS as WS Server
    participant R as Redis/BullMQ
    participant DB as PostgreSQL

    B->>N: Checkout (Server Action)
    N->>DB: Create Order + Payment (status: pending)
    N->>M: Create Snap Token / Core API Charge
    M-->>N: Token + Payment URL
    N->>WS: POST /jobs/schedule (expire-payment, 24h)
    WS->>R: Add delayed job to queue
    N-->>B: Redirect ke payment page

    B->>M: User bayar
    M->>N: Webhook POST /api/midtrans/notification
    N->>N: Verify signature SHA512
    N->>DB: Update payment.status = 'paid', order.status = 'processing'
    N->>WS: POST /jobs/schedule (cancel-expire-payment)
    WS->>R: Remove delayed job
    N->>DB: Create notification record
    N->>WS: POST /emit (notifications, store:X, new-order)
    WS-->>B: Socket.IO → Toast + Sound + Badge update
```

### 4.2. Alur Pengiriman (Biteship)

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant Courier as Biteship/Kurir
    participant N as Next.js
    participant DB as PostgreSQL
    participant WS as WS Server
    participant R as Redis/BullMQ
    participant B as Browser (Buyer)

    Courier->>N: Webhook POST /api/biteship/webhook
    N->>N: Verify x-biteship-signature
    N->>DB: Update shipment.status & order.status
    N->>DB: Create notification record
    N->>WS: POST /emit (notification → user:buyerId)
    WS-->>B: Socket.IO → Real-time update

    alt Status = "delivered"
        N->>WS: POST /jobs/schedule (auto-complete, 7 hari)
        WS->>R: Add delayed job
        Note over R: Setelah 7 hari...
        R->>WS: BullMQ Worker processes job
        WS->>DB: order.status = 'completed' + tambah saldo seller + update soldCount
    end
```

### 4.3. Alur Chat Real-Time

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant A as User A (Browser)
    participant WS as WS Server
    participant B as User B (Browser)
    participant N as Next.js
    participant DB as PostgreSQL

    A->>WS: socket.emit("join-conversation", {id: 1})
    B->>WS: socket.emit("join-conversation", {id: 1})

    A->>WS: socket.emit("send-message", {convId: 1, message: ...})
    WS-->>B: socket.emit("new-message", {...}) [broadcast ke room]
    
    A->>N: Server Action: saveMessage() [simpan ke DB]
    N->>DB: INSERT INTO messages (...)
    
    A->>WS: socket.emit("typing", {convId: 1, isTyping: true})
    WS-->>B: socket.emit("user-typing", {...})
```

> [!NOTE]
> Chat menggunakan pola **"optimistic relay"**:
> - WS Server hanya sebagai **relay/pemancar** — broadcast pesan ke room
> - **Penyimpanan data** dilakukan oleh client melalui Next.js Server Action
> - Ini memisahkan tanggung jawab: WS = speed, Next.js = persistence

### 4.4. Alur Notifikasi Real-Time

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant B as Browser
    participant NP as NotificationProvider
    participant WS as WS Server
    participant N as Next.js

    B->>NP: Mount (layout level)
    NP->>NP: Extract session token dari cookie
    NP->>WS: Connect /notifications (auth: sessionToken)
    WS->>WS: Verify session via PostgreSQL
    WS->>WS: Auto-join room user:{userId}

    Note over N: Event terjadi (webhook, action)
    N->>WS: POST /emit (notifications, user:X, "notification", data)
    WS-->>NP: socket.on("notification", data)
    NP->>NP: Update React Query cache (unread count + list)
    NP->>NP: Toast + Sound + BroadcastChannel
    NP->>NP: Invalidate related queries (orders, tracking)
```

