## 5. Fair Rank System (Scoring Algorithm)

File: [score-calculator.js](file:///c:/Putra/Ngoding%20AntiGravity/set-ecomerce/kirimart/ws-server/src/jobs/score-calculator.js)

Berjalan sebagai **cron job BullMQ setiap 6 jam** di WS Server.

**Formula Score:**

| Komponen | Max | Detail |
|----------|-----|--------|
| **Product Quality** | 40 | Rating (15) + Review count (10) + Sold count (10) + Discount (5) |
| **Store Reputation** | 40 | Rating (15) + Verified (10) + Reviews (10) + Complaint penalty (-5) |
| **Activity Bonus** | 20 | Active voucher (5) + Profile completeness (5) + Fresh product (5) |
| **Freshness Boost** | 30 | Produk baru < 7 hari mendapat boost linear |
| **Randomizer** | 10 | Hash-based pseudo-random per 6 jam (anti-monopoli) |
| **Total** | ~140 | Skor disimpan di `products.visibility_score` |

Setelah kalkulasi, Redis cache `cache:products:*` di-invalidate.

