## 6. Keamanan & Proteksi

### Route Protection ([proxy.js](file:///c:/Putra/Ngoding%20AntiGravity/set-ecomerce/kirimart/src/proxy.js))

| Rule | Route | Aksi |
|------|-------|------|
| Closed routes | (configurable) | Redirect ke `/` |
| Auth routes | `/sign-in`, `/sign-up` | Redirect ke `/` jika sudah login |
| Admin routes | `/admin-dashboard/*` | Harus login + role = `admin` |
| Seller routes | `/seller-dashboard/*` | Harus login + role = `seller` |
| Protected routes | `/create-store/*` | Harus login (any role) |

### Inter-Service Security

| Komunikasi | Mekanisme |
|------------|-----------|
| Next.js → WS Server | Header `x-ws-secret` (shared secret) |
| Browser → WS Server | Session token verification via PostgreSQL |
| Midtrans → Next.js | SHA512 signature verification |
| Biteship → Next.js | Custom header signature |
| Next.js → Midtrans | HTTP Basic Auth (Base64 encoded Server Key) |

