## 7. Cara Menjalankan Aplikasi — Step by Step

### Prasyarat
- **Node.js** 22+ 
- **Bun** (package manager & runtime)
- **Docker Desktop** (untuk Redis & WS Server)
- **PostgreSQL** terinstall di Windows (port 5432)
- **Ngrok** (untuk expose webhook ke internet)

### Step 1: Start PostgreSQL
```bash
# Pastikan PostgreSQL service berjalan di Windows
# Database: kirimart, User: postgres, Password: root
```

### Step 2: Start Docker Containers (Redis + WS Server)
```bash
cd c:\Putra\Ngoding AntiGravity\set-ecomerce\kirimart

# Pertama kali (build image WS Server):
docker compose up --build -d

# Selanjutnya (tanpa rebuild):
docker compose up -d

# Cek status:
docker compose ps
# Expected: kirimart-redis (healthy), kirimart-ws (healthy)
```

### Step 3: Start File Uploader Service
```bash
cd c:\Putra\Ngoding\MyFundAction-V2-New\file-uploader
npm start
# Berjalan di port 4004
```

### Step 4: Start Next.js Development Server
```bash
cd c:\Putra\Ngoding AntiGravity\set-ecomerce\kirimart
bun dev
# Berjalan di port 3000
# Menggunakan --webpack flag (bukan turbopack)
```

### Step 5: Start Ngrok Tunnel (untuk webhook)
```bash
ngrok http --domain=unintermingled-noncoincident-chandler.ngrok-free.app 3000
# Mengexpose localhost:3000 ke URL publik
# Webhook Midtrans & Biteship mengarah ke URL ini
```

